## AUTO-DIFF TRIGGER

Trigger diff automatically when BOTH fileA and fileB are set.
Use useEffect:
```typescript
useEffect(() => {
  if (fileA && fileB && fileAContent && fileBContent) {
    runDiff()
  }
}, [fileA, fileB, primaryKeys, ignoreColumns])
```

runDiff() calls cmd_diff_csv with current config.
Also runs when primaryKeys or ignoreColumns change
(user changed settings in popup and re-runs).

Auto-detect primary key on each file drop:
When fileA loads → setPrimaryKeys(fileA.primaryKeyCandidates.slice(0,1))
If fileB loads first → setPrimaryKeys(fileB.primaryKeyCandidates.slice(0,1))
If both loaded → keep fileA's candidates as authoritative

